LDING 701', N'Ghế Sofa Gỗ Tràm Tự Nhiên MOHO KOLDING 701', CAST(N'2022-10-27T14:39:00' AS SmallDateTime), 1, CAST(N'2023-03-22T22:44:00' AS SmallDateTime), 1, 1, 0)
